data.description: Welcome to this stunning open concept home with 4 large size bedrooms and 2 remodeled bathrooms. This home has some new amazing upgrades including new recessed lighting in the kitchen and living room area, AC unit recently maintenance , also all the crown moldings have been repainted and redone. New backsplash has been added in kitchen cooking area, master bathroom flooring redone. All rooms in the living area have also been upgraded with luxury vinyl flooring. The kitchen was recently updated with white modern cabinetry, granite countertops, and fresh coat of paint. This home also has a long driveway leading to a spacious backyard and gated iron fence in the front for extra security. New landscape has also been added in the front yard and garden beds. Solar is included but leased. Won't last long! Book your showing today!
